{"tid":224623,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你地點抽時間睇書?","createTime":"2017-05-01T08:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T12:58:57.000Z","uid":79314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c57a06d00e0bb5a83453cb96feca38de07f7786","tid":224623,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"平日返工放工, 係車到都累到訓<br />\n返到屋企沖個涼食個飯都差唔多要訓<br />\n訓前睇書又會失眠 (眼好累但個腦會狂諗野)<br />\n星期六日做下其他野又冇左時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到睇一本書拖左好耐<br />\n但又忍唔住成日想買書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實係我體力差定係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知大家點抽時間睇書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c2ab7e182afea873e899d469217bf583d3f3c5","tid":224623,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e9c3779759b8901798ed6ae5c22677b614c0759","tid":224623,"uid":87030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:07:25.000Z","msg":"搭車時間，睇到就睇，腿訓就睇到訓，一日睇10版英文書（來回個半鐘）"},{"pid":"410757cc7eeda5bdba3d8e056627060f9197d284","tid":224623,"uid":30892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"睇書會失眠？睇電話電腦更甚"},{"pid":"142ca22266723a445373edcb4e6ff3ba8c797499","tid":224623,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇書會失眠？睇電話電腦更甚</blockquote><br />\n睇書先易瞓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f5f485f91415b80dc6f2fcfa33780e6850eddb","tid":224623,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:20:38.000Z","msg":"搭車個段時間睇，有時係會睇睇下訓著左<br />\n輕小說<br />\n<br />\n呢個習慣keep左起碼8-9年<br />\n但睇書既速度點都唔夠我買書既速度"},{"pid":"690b117227d4d6dfcdd5fb104b6315e2564c1725","tid":224623,"uid":48874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"買部kindle <br />\n坐車睇"},{"pid":"82d9a26ab77f3f03aca43385235107be8f1850d7","tid":224623,"uid":59327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日睇香港加World News都已經冇咩時間"},{"pid":"ffa7eca744f26d1032a97482556a2f25943c5754","tid":224623,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"當資料睇，每個月都比自己一個問題去做research<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇論文多過書"}]}